testsuite.name: com.tvd.eqx.service.ServiceRoutesSpec

testcase.name: The main routing service should return a pong for GET ping request
The main routing service should return a MethodNotAllowed error for PUT ping requests where PUT is not implemented
The main routing service should return for GET healthcheck request for database status
The main routing service should return for GET healthcheck request for memory status
The main routing service should return successfully for POST log request with level and path query parameters
The main routing service should return a missing path query parameter rejection when the parameter path is not supplied
The main routing service should return successfully for GET log level request with path query parameter
The main routing service should return empty users when DB empty for GET all the users
The main routing service should create a new user in an empty DB
The main routing service should return one user for GET the user by username
The main routing service should create the second user in the DB
The main routing service should return two users for GET all the users
The main routing service should delete one user by id
The main routing service should update an existing user
The main routing service should return a not found message for GET with only slash
The main routing service should return a not found error message for GET in the path prefix eqx with slash
The main routing service should return a not found error message for GET in the path prefix eqx without slash
The main routing service should return a not found error message for GET of a non-existing path
